      "input": "EIGRP-IPv4 Neighbors for AS(215)\nH   Address                 Interface              Hold Uptime   SRTT   RTO  Q  Seq\n                                                   (sec)         (ms)       Cnt Num\n1   81.211.127.255          Tu5                      13 18:52:46   55   330  0  1042408760\n   Version 25.0/2.0, Retrans: 1, Retries: 0, Prefixes: 952\n   Topology-ids from peer - 0\n0   83.151.157.254          Tu5                      12 6d08h      50   300  0  564418354\n   Version 25.0/2.0, Retrans: 6, Retries: 0, Prefixes: 952\n   Topology-ids from peer - 0\nMax Nbrs: 0, Current Nbrs: 0\n",
      "expected": {
        "neighbors": {
          "Tunnel5": {
            "81.211.127.255": {
              "handle": 1,
              "hold_time": 13,
              "prefixes": 952,
              "queue_count": 0,
              "retransmit_count": 1,
              "retry_count": 0,
